name: La Bomba - Canelo Alvarez vs. Caleb Plant 2021
description: At a sold-out MGM Grand Garden Arena, Canelo went 11 rounds with Plant and finished the fight via TKO. Canelo goes on to unify all four 168-pound titles and become the WBA, WBC, WBO, and new IBF Champion. La leyenda continua.. | @thesportsdoodle
